---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Juicy AI">
  <div class="bg-base-100 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-base-content sm:text-5xl">
          About Juicy AI
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-base-content/70">
          Welcome to my corner of the internet where AI meets creativity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Hello, I'm the creator of Juicy AI</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-4">
          I'm passionate about artificial intelligence, machine learning, and the incredible ways 
          technology is reshaping our world. This blog is my space to share insights, experiments, 
          and discoveries from the fascinating intersection of AI and everyday life.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">
          Whether you're a fellow AI enthusiast, a developer looking to dive into machine learning, 
          or simply curious about the future of technology, you'll find something interesting here.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold mr-2">•</span>
          <span>Deep dives into AI technologies and their practical applications</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold mr-2">•</span>
          <span>Tutorials and guides for developers and AI enthusiasts</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold mr-2">•</span>
          <span>Thoughts on the future of technology and its impact on society</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold mr-2">•</span>
          <span>Reviews of AI tools, frameworks, and emerging technologies</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        I love connecting with fellow AI enthusiasts and curious minds. Feel free to reach out 
        if you have questions, ideas for collaboration, or just want to chat about the latest 
        in AI and tech.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-base-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-base-content/80 italic">
          "The best way to predict the future is to create it." - This philosophy drives 
          everything I do here at Juicy AI. Let's build the future together, one algorithm at a time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>